OL,5, A rising number of households are      
OL,6, having their energy smart meters       
OL,7, remotely switched to prepayment meters,
OL,8, the energy regulator has said.         
OL,10,FEnergy firms can use the technology to 
OL,11,Fswap customers in debt to the more     
OL,12,Fcostly plan without needing a warrant. 
OL,14,FOfgem said it had received reports of  
OL,15,F"vulnerable customers being left       
OL,16,Fwithout power for days or even weeks". 
OL,18,FKelly, from South London, whose meter  
OL,19,Fwas switched, said: "I suddenly only   
OL,20,Fhad #3 on my electric until payday."   
